com.alibaba.mtc

Class MtContextCallable<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alibaba.mtc.MtContextCallable<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable<V>

    public final class MtContextCallable<V>
extends Object
implements Callable<V>
    MtContextCallable decorate Callable, so as to get MtContextThreadLocal and transmit it to the time of Callable execution, needed when use Callable to thread pool.

    Use factory method get(Callable) to get decorated instance.

    Since:
    0.9.0
    Author:
    ding.lid
    See Also:
    Executor, ExecutorService, ThreadPoolExecutor, ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor, Executors, CompletionService, ExecutorCompletionService
